org.chocosolver.solver.search.loop.lns.neighbors

Class ExplainingObjective

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.chocosolver.solver.search.loop.lns.neighbors.ExplainingCut
      • org.chocosolver.solver.search.loop.lns.neighbors.ExplainingObjective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INeighbor

    public class ExplainingObjective
extends ExplainingCut
    a specific neighborhood for LNS based on the explanation of the objective variable.

    This neightborhood is specific in the sense that it needs to compute explanation on a solution. Furthermore, the fixSomeVariables method creates and applies decision, so that the explanation recorder can infer.

    Since:
    03/07/13
    Author:
    Charles Prud'homme
